Radarfigure with updated hot keys:

w,a,s,d move pick window around
r - toggle bottom button
t - toggle top button
y - full view
u - autopick
i - save pick
b - set zoom in (typically good for bed picking)
m - higher zoom in (typically good for detailed picking)

1-9 set bounds with variable width (top pick at cursor location)
c - cross picks
v - delete picks 




K - lock/unlock crosshair (feature has to be activated first - check box)
L - lock/unlock trace  (feature has to be activated first - check box)
